Description:
LOCATION! PRIME! WHAT ELSE DO YOU WANT!
Are you looking for a titled land in the most after Derrimut? This is your answer! Great entry for first home buyers or investors!
With 12.5m frontage and a depth of 31m, this prime piece of land is a great opportunity to buy into the booming suburb of Derrimut. There's the new Derrimut Shopping Centre and only walking distance! Also, the Deer Park Train Station is so close. Schools are within short distance.
Mt. Derrimut Road is really booming with lots of shops emerging! Cafes, restaurants, gym, education centre, Chemist Warehouse, furniture shop, carwash and many more!
Easy access to the city, Melbourne Airport via Western Ring Road and all amenities! Lots of ongoing infrastucture! This area is just booming!

Description:
Right Where You Want To Be!
Situated in a highly sought after residential pocket is this surprisingly spacious family home representing a super buy for owner occupiers and investors alike. Comprising four bedrooms (2 with WIRs and 2 with BIRs), master with ensuite, open plan living & dining area, functional kitchen, family room, bright central bathroom and laundry. The home has been freshly painted & carpeted throughout. Features include; ducted heating, alarm system, double garage with internal access and established gardens. Just a stones throw away from Derrimut Primary School, community centre, sporting facilities, transport as well as nearby shops this is definitely one to add to your list.
